          "message": {
            "text": "Improper output handling \u2014 SSRF via LLM-synthesized URL: the Orchestrator can instruct the MCP Tool Server to fetch external URLs synthesized from LLM output. An attacker who influences the Orchestrator's output can cause it to emit internal service URLs (cloud metadata endpoints, internal admin APIs) as tool parameters. The Tool Server fetches these with its server-side network credentials. Execution context is **server-side**: the HTTP client runs with the Tool Server's IAM role.",
